<subparagraph id="H698E8A76CE0B4B9EBF684AD73C2F5794" commented="no">
                  <enum>(T)</enum>
                  <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">provide technical assistance and training to State and local law enforcement agencies and statewide clearinghouses to coordinate with State and local educational agencies in identifying and recovering missing children;</text>
                </subparagraph> 
<subparagraph id="HFC9D1804899543FF823EB82F3B2D02F9">
                  <enum>(U)</enum>
